INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (1,1,'Mr WordPress','','https://wordpress.org/','','2015-06-02 18:53:00','2015-06-02 18:53:00','Hi, this is a comment.\nTo delete a comment, just log in and view the post&#039;s comments. There you will have the option to edit or delete them.',0,'1','','',0,0),(2,75,'Priya','gaurav.amte@gmail.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-06-24 18:02:00','2014-06-24 12:32:00','Really inspired by the work you are doing. We need to teach our government some lessons.',0,'1','','',0,0),(3,75,'yagvendra','vankibonal@gmail.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-07-28 21:14:00','2014-07-28 15:44:00','i also support your work',0,'1','','',0,0),(4,75,'helpiez','helpiezteam@gmail.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-08-01 16:25:00','2014-08-01 10:55:00','Thanks a lot Yagvendra! We really care for your support.',0,'1','','',3,0),(5,75,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','59.177.15.181','2014-11-30 17:20:00','2014-11-30 11:50:00','good going man thankx for sharing',0,'1','','',0,0),(6,1475,'dazi','vankibbonal@gmail.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-09-23 12:59:00','2014-09-23 07:29:00','you can check your body protein need here \n\nhttp://www.meals.com/cooking-with-nestle/food-tools-calculators/protein-calculator',0,'1','','',0,0),(7,1575,'gaurav jain','gauravjain.coolguy@yahoo.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-11-09 20:17:00','2014-11-09 14:47:00','Wonderfully written article !!',0,'1','','',0,0),(8,1631,'Nitesh Krishna Punnani','niteshkrishna5@gmail.com','','37.228.106.110','2014-11-21 14:05:00','2014-11-21 08:35:00','hey Anu u just done the great job... every line is so much meaning full.... this shows ur kind towards orphans... its amazing... al the best... keep going... there is very long way fr u... :)',0,'1','','',0,0),(9,1631,'Somasree Choudhury','somasree1211@gmail.com','','202.62.237.98','2014-11-22 01:13:00','2014-11-21 19:43:00','A Good Read.\nJust a thought..\nApart from the fact that these orphanages need a lot of donation both in cash and kind, the herculean task is to ensure that these donations are actually used for the welfare of the children and are not gobbled up by the intermediaries. I think there should be some effective mechanism to supervise the whole affair.',0,'1','','',0,0),(10,1631,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','59.177.5.63','2014-11-24 00:35:00','2014-11-23 19:05:00','nice...good way of putting thoughts in so simple way',0,'1','','',0,0),(11,1631,'Grace Bains','gracebains05@gmail.com','','59.180.146.84','2014-11-30 02:46:00','2014-11-29 21:16:00','The sad part is that there are so many other children just like that.\nReally,  it was a touching story',0,'1','','',0,0),(12,1631,'gaurav jain','gauravjain.coolguy@yahoo.com','','103.27.8.44','2014-12-20 16:42:00','2014-12-20 16:42:00','Really a Heart-Touching article  .......',0,'1','','',0,0),(13,1665,'Gautam Sagar','gautam0sikdar@gmail.com','','120.56.232.137','2014-11-23 00:15:00','2014-11-22 18:45:00','nice man....... Misfortune is sometime time good for our own sake',0,'1','','',0,0),(14,1665,'Gautam Sikdar','gautam0sagar@gmail.com','','120.56.232.137','2014-11-23 00:24:00','2014-11-22 18:54:00','Sweet are the uses of adversity,\n\nWhich, like the toad, ugly and venomous,\n\nWears yet a precious jewel in his head;\n\nAnd this our life, exempt from public haunt,\n\nFinds tongues in trees, books in the running brooks,\n\nSermons in stones, and good in every thing.--- shakespeare\'s... but it might be applicable with every misfortune',0,'1','','',0,0),(15,1665,'Meerarajukumar','meerarajukumar@gmail.com','','14.97.169.230','2014-11-23 09:01:00','2014-11-23 03:31:00','This is very true. Ultimately difficulties faced by a person is what makes him/her stronger. As Swami Vivekananda said \" In a day when you don\'t come across any problems, you can be sure that you are travelling in the wrong path\"  It is our duty to make the most of these misfortunes and learn from them.',0,'1','','',0,0),(16,1665,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','120.56.128.41','2014-11-24 00:24:00','2014-11-23 18:54:00','Thank you Gautam sagar , Meerarajukumar and Gautam sikdar for your review :)',0,'1','','',0,0),(17,1665,'Suveer Garg','gargsuveer@gmail.com','','14.139.251.107','2014-11-28 20:14:00','2014-11-28 14:44:00','I totally agree with your opinion. Adversities add spice to life. If you have not faced an adversity , you cannot appreciate luxury.',0,'1','','',0,0),(18,1665,'Grace Bains','gracebains05@gmail.com','','59.180.146.84','2014-11-30 02:49:00','2014-11-29 21:19:00','This reminds me of Tennyson\'s poem Ullyseis where he says \'one equal temperament for all heroic hearts\'\nWe should all be striving to accept the whole concept of yin and yang -there\'s something good in everything that seems bad\n',0,'1','','',0,0),(19,1665,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','120.57.130.161','2014-12-28 18:06:00','2014-12-28 18:06:00','it just a misfortune that give us that spark for some more fortune',0,'1','','',0,0),(20,1702,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','120.56.128.41','2014-11-24 00:29:00','2014-11-23 18:59:00','We are looking forward to achieve these promises.....our Prime Minister can do that',0,'1','','',0,0),(21,1702,'Rishika Sharma','rishika.chandra@gmail.com','','14.96.208.126','2014-11-24 15:23:00','2014-11-24 09:53:00','Definitely sir, as a writer,I feel great pride in bringing out this visionary man\'s great ideas! Hope each one sees it\'s achievement soon!',0,'1','','',0,0),(22,1708,'Rajni Dubey','dubey.rajni28feb@gmail.com','','117.247.198.48','2014-11-24 18:46:00','2014-11-24 13:16:00','Thought provoking :)',0,'1','','',0,0),(23,1708,'Keshav Sikdar','keshav0sikdar@gmail.com','','59.177.15.181','2014-11-30 17:01:00','2014-11-30 11:31:00','nice written.... according to me, we need to start from start, from childhood. I can\'t change myself its my socially constructed nature that  i can\'t even reform my masculinity  because it starts from our childhood, where we had learned the basic gender characteristi